title: Amanqaku abalulekileyo kunye nokukhankanywa-iTempile ye-Orbital
heading: Amanqaku abalulekileyo kunye nokukhankanywa
description: Lo mzobo weminyaka emininzi uyinxalenye ye-13 ye-Mercosul Bienal ePorto Alegre, eBrazil, egcinwe nguMarcelo Dantas. Ifakwe kuluhlu olude kwiBhaso le-Lumen 2022-iMbasa yekamva. Kwakhona iphumelele iCandelo le-ArtSat lokhuphiswano lweCubeDesign 2021, olukhuthazwa yiBrazilian Institute of Space Research (INPE).
